  <brief_title>Study Evaluating Single Ascending Doses of MR1817</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Study Investigating the Safety, Tolerability, Pharmacokinetics, and Pharmacodynamics of Ascending Single Doses of Orally Administered MR1817 in Healthy Adult Subjects</official_title>
  <sponsors>
