  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a first-in-human study of MR1817. This study will provide an initial assessment of
      the safety, tolerability, pharmacokinetics (PK), and pharmacodynamics (PD) of MR1817 after
      administration of ascending single oral doses to healthy adult subjects.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
